                    In addition, I have also gotten as many as 3 spirits responding to your question at the same time.  I believe Bruce and Steve have experienced that on more than one occasion.  Maybe they could post or attach one of these files for an example.  

                    They know whats going on, and they will comply with you and guide you along the way.  Best of Luck and Great Job!

